query:
/*+ NoNestLoop(hd ss td s) */ select count(*)
from time_dim AS td
inner join store_sales AS ss
on ss.ss_sold_time_sk = td.t_time_sk AND td.t_hour = 20 AND td.t_minute >= 30
inner join household_demographics AS hd
on ss.ss_hdemo_sk = hd.hd_demo_sk AND hd.hd_dep_count = 5
inner join store AS s
on ss.ss_store_sk = s.s_store_sk AND s.s_store_name = 'ese' order by count(*) LIMIT 100;
